{"tid":1196960,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝搭過海巴士經過灣仔中環暢通無阻！！！","createTime":"2019-06-10T00:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T02:36:36.000Z","uid":26322,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"117bdc431f5f8a3c193b881d3b91390e1fad7ee0","tid":1196960,"uid":26322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:51:02.000Z","msg":"話說今朝返工，諗緊搭地鐵定巴士好。平時都係搭巴士，但琴日中環有大型嬉戲活動諗緊會唔會好似5年前咁塞咗條路。<br />\n<br />\n事實證明最後選擇搭巴士係正確的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人好波！！！夠哂和平，琴晚玩完今朝繼續返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府大時大節特別有效率，香港政府好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392c18557136907f1fea82e17e939f7a72acd73b","tid":1196960,"uid":26322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258a62a2c05b3005b8a2f5406b7680424416f861","tid":1196960,"uid":252295,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:52:42.000Z","msg":"琴晚發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？ 咪星期日咯"},{"pid":"297a65de3ffc3cf4937e15a590577c64da0e77dc","tid":1196960,"uid":26322,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"258a62a2c05b3005b8a2f5406b7680424416f861","tid":1196960,"uid":252295,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:52:42.000Z","msg":"琴晚發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？ 咪星期日咯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:54:33.000Z","msg":"星期日梗係要行下街打下卡，同末係人多啲，不過出完街就梗係要返屋企第二日繼續返工返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab613b29108a268e74482eb7ed45e9ec213fb244","tid":1196960,"uid":26322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:57:58.000Z","msg":"準時返到公司啦，仲早咗添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe0e0aec9262fa6f92b3008997839d6